'''天主教巴勒延戈代教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Palayamkottaiensis}}；{{lang-en|Diocese of Palayamkottai}}）是[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]的一個[[教區|教區]]，位於[[印度|印度]][[泰米爾納德邦|泰米爾納德邦]]南部，受[[天主教馬杜賴總教區|馬杜賴總教區]]管轄。

教區成立於1973年6月12日。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=[[宗座公報|宗座公報]]|publisher=[[梵蒂岡出版社|梵蒂岡出版社]]|date=1973年|volume=65|title=Romani Pontifices|page=484|url=http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2065%20%5B1973%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf|access-date=2013-12-22|archive-date=2013-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130303053335/http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2065%20[1973]%20-%20ocr.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>2004年有教友123,789名，佔轄區總人口百分之4.7。由七十八名司鐸名管理三十八個堂區。現任教區主教為{{link-de|安滕尼薩米·舍沃里穆圖|Antonysamy Savarimuthu}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 20.11.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/20/191120d.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-11-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191120130940/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/20/191120d.html |archivedate=2019-11-20 |language=en |date=2019-11-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-de|猶達·吉拉·保羅拉傑|Jude Gerald Paulraj}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 02.07.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/07/02/180702b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-11-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191120145304/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/07/02/180702b.html |archivedate=2019-11-20 |language=en |date=2018-07-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

